{"type":null,"faqId":48072,"title":"时钟","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">使用闹钟</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"添加闹钟\"XE \"启用闹钟\"XE \"设置闹钟再响间隔\"XE \"删除闹钟\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178071\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“时钟”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>在“闹钟”页签下，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>添加闹钟：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178072\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，设置闹钟响铃的时间，重复周期及铃声等，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178073\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>开启/关闭闹钟：点击闹钟旁边的开关，开启或关闭闹钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>设置闹钟：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178074\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，设置闹钟的再响间隔、静音模式下闹钟是否响铃以及按音量键是否关闭闹钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>删除闹钟：长按要删除的闹钟，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178075\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span><a name=\"_task_use_world_clock-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">使用世界时钟</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"世界时钟\"XE \"添加城市\"XE \"设置时区\"XE \"删除城市\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178076\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“时钟”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>2.在“时钟”页签下，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>添加城市：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178077\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，输入城市名称，或从城市列表中选择城市。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>设置时区：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178078\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，设置家中的时区以及系统日期和时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>删除城市：点击“编辑城市”，点击要删除城市旁边的“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178079\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178080\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span><a name=\"_task_use_stop_watch-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">使用秒表</span><span>XE \"秒表计时\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178081\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“时钟”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.在“秒表”页签下，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178082\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”启动计时。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>在计时过程中，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178083\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”可以进行次数统计。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178084\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”暂停计时。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">后续处理</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>停止计时后，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178085\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”清空计时记录。</span><a name=\"_task_use_timer-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">使用计时器</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"计时器\"XE \"倒计时\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178086\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“时钟”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>2.在“计时”页签下，滑动转盘选择计时时长。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178087\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178088\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，可以选择计时响铃提示音。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>3.设置完成后，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178089\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，计时器开始倒计时。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>4.手机通过响铃提示计时结束。按照屏幕提示，滑动屏幕停止响铃。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178090\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>在计时过程中，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178091\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，计时时长归零。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3658","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Convenient-features","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598110000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":36,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}